author: wn.com
title: Election night in Ottawa comes down to suburban vote
text: The story of the 2015 campaign in Ottawa boils down to the fight for suburban seats in what could be seen as the capital’s version of the 905 area code around Toronto, a ring running from Kanata to Orléans, where retirements and riding redistributions have changed the calculations since the 2011 vote. ...
